data.description: GEORGEOUS SUPER CLEAN PATIO/DUPLEX HOME IN WONDERFUL NEIGHBORHOOD CLOSE TO ERIE ,  LAFAYETTE, AND BROOMFIELD. SELLERS ADDED OVER $100,000 IN UPGRADES WHEN THEY PURCHASED PROPERTY NEW.  THERE ARE MANY BUILT IN DELUXE CUSTOM CABINETS IN KITCHEN, BATHS,LAUNDRY, BUILT IN BAR AREA, AND ENTERTAINMENT CENTER IN BASEMENT. THERE ARE SPEAKERS BUILT IN THROUGHOUT THE HOME. MR. AND MRS. CLEAN LIVED HERE, NEVER WORE SHOES IN HOUSE. THIS HOME IS LOADED WITH EXTRAS. DELUXE KITCHEN CABINETS WITH PULL OUT SHELVES, COOK TOP IN ISLAND, CABINET BUILT IN OVEN AND MICROWAVE. THE MAIN FLOOR OFFICE HAS GOOD LIGHTING. CUSTOM WINDOW COVERINGS THROUGHOUT, GAS FIREPLACE. BEAUTIFUL BUILDER FINISHED BASEMENT WITH BUILT IN CABINETS, WET BAR,  WINE RACK AND COOLER. SURROUND SOUND ,RECEIVER, AND TV INCLUDED. OF COURSE HOME IS LOADED WITH CUSTOM GRANITE,TILE, AND DELUXE CARPET. CLOSE TO GOLF COURSE.LARGE REAR TREX PATIO WITH SPEAKERS AND INCLUDED BBQ. GARAGE HAS NICE WORK BENCH AND CABINETS. BETTER HURRY ON THIS ONE. BUYERS SHOULD CONTACT HOA'S  FOR COMPLETE LIST OF AMENITIES AND EXTERIOR MAINTENANCE ITEMS PROVIDED BY HOA. HOA#1 IS HERITAGE AT VISTA RIDGE. PHONE IS 720-974-4167.  HOA#2 IS VISTA RIDGE AT SAME PHONE NUMBER. BOTH ARE MANAGED BY MSI. BUYERS SHOULD DO ANY AND ALL INSPECTIONS THEY DESIRE PRIOR TO PURCHASE.
